1990): f233-8[13] Moore TJ, Crantz FR, Hollenberg NK "Contribution of prostaglandins to the antihypertensive action of captopril in essential hypertension." Hypertension 3 (1981): 168-73[14] Ray K, Dorman S, Watson R "Severe hyperkalaemia due to the concomitant use of salt substitutes and ACE inhibitors in hypertension: a potentially life threatening interaction." J Hum Hypertens 13 (1999): 717-20[15] "Product Information. Vasotec (enalapril)." Merck & Co, Inc, West Point, PA.[16] Good CB, McDermott L "Diet and serum potassium in patients on ACE inhibitors." JAMA 274 (1995): 538', 1767365203);
